# Digital Notes App

A simple notes management web application built using **Python, Flask, and SQLite**.

## Features
- Create, update, and delete notes
- Search notes
- SQLite database
- REST API
- Responsive UI

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Flask
- SQLite
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript

## Run the Project

```bash
git clone https://github.com/JyothiPeddireddy/Digital_Notes_App.git
cd Digital_Notes_App
pip install flask
python app.py
```

Open: `http://127.0.0.1:5000`

## What I Learned
- Flask REST APIs
- CRUD operations
- SQLite database
- Frontend and backend integration


